Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:25.38,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:30.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:35.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:46.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:52.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:54.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:02:01.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:05.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:11.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:16.38,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:29.69,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:25.38,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:30.81,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:35.59,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.84,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:46.87,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:52.56,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:54.72,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:02:01.58,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:05.19,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:11.98,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:16.38,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.96,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.63,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.66,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:29.69,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.03,0:46:27.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}割り切れない想いを力に変えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.53,0:46:31.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無謀だと笑われた　何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.91,0:46:35.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}毎日が冒険で　青春で
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.75,0:46:40.50,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい音と出会っては磨いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.50,0:46:44.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}本気でやったからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.91,0:46:49.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こわい瞬間もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.22,0:46:50.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.11,0:46:50.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.93,0:46:51.73,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でたい
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.75,0:46:52.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.51,0:46:57.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一度息を吹き込む　明日へと
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.68,0:47:01.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}タクトに導かれてここまで来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.52,0:47:05.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.57,0:47:08.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でているのは人生だ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.07,0:47:09.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響くのは感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.95,0:47:14.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと忘れないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.99,0:47:18.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}光る音が涙を照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.79,0:47:23.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛いことばかりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.25,0:47:28.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だっていつも　いつも楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.79,0:47:30.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そうでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.68,0:47:34.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！歌え　五線の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.76,0:47:41.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！響け　遠くの春に
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.03,0:46:27.53,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春的苦涩变为了前进的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.53,0:46:31.91,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}年少冲动让我无数次被嘲笑声掩埋
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.91,0:46:35.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天都在冒险　挥洒青春
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.75,0:46:40.50,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断磨练期待与新的乐声邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.50,0:46:44.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为全身心的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.91,0:46:49.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自然会有害怕的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.22,0:46:50.03,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要传递
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.11,0:46:50.93,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要触及
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.93,0:46:51.73,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.75,0:46:52.51,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.51,0:46:57.39,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次向着奏响的明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.68,0:47:01.52,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遵循指挥棒的指引来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.52,0:47:05.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手一起
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.57,0:47:08.03,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正在奏响的是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.07,0:47:09.95,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}余音缭绕的是情感
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.95,0:47:14.99,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.99,0:47:18.79,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的乐声将我们的泪水照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.79,0:47:23.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并非全是辛酸经历
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.25,0:47:28.77,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为　一路走来有许多快乐伴随着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.79,0:47:30.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.68,0:47:34.39,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！于五线谱之上唱响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.76,0:47:41.44,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！向着远处胜利的春天吹响吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午开始合奏练习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉　这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍纪念照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  摆好姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么站在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奖状谁来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐  请把头再低下去点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  摆万岁的姿势来拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份喜悦要用全身来表现才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高兴是很高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  总觉得还有些难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么实感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家摆个姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北宇治高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吹奏乐竞赛会京都府大赛中获得了金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还将作为代表出席关西大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:22.46,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}盛夏的fanfare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了大家  集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…因为这种事我还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道该说些什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  祝贺你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  应该我们感谢老师才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊是  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不热烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从今天这一刻起就是代表了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不愧对这个身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须进一步锻炼演奏水平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们从此时此刻起就带上这份觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说学校的吹奏乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一个顾问就能变得大有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到竟然能去关西大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松本老师也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来这里赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次听到他们演奏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道他们是有潜力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中世古同学和田中同学拥有不输强校的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上高坂同学和川岛同学的加入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身边有了如此优秀的榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就看他们是否耳濡目染了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说还有成长的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还有很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有个请求…想和您商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都拿到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便什么也没写  来练习也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片空白的计划表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:07:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正意味着之后我们将有个和暑假想去甚远的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8月的17  18  19这三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会借附近的设施进行集训
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天回去以后请和家人好好说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前的15  16的休息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也非常想练习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但学校规定这段期间一定要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自主练习也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校好像会关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在为大赛拼搏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能去关西大赛这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让全国大赛从梦想变为了真实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  所剩的时间有限
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年级不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年级  一年级也不要认为还有明年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好抓住这次的机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…祝贺大家出席关西大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Monaka队也会向着关西大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往地支持大家  共同活跃这个部的氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请听我们满怀祝贺的演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Congratulation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变熟练了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长  你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家明明也很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  这时候要说些有干劲的话做结尾才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  开始喽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北宇治Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}那是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样北宇治高中吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向着关西大赛迈出了第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绿我太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定练习了不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然听得出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Monaka的各位一起商量好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要竭尽所能做好我们能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1470,1060)}丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,1060)}高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂同学不是骑自行车上下学的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「妈妈排球」？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以她想要每天去太阳公园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把我的自行车借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公园？去那里都是上坡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也说了让她买带电力辅助的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是充满活力的妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们最近能一起回家了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我有时会因为组练晚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等你  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的结束时间也是各不相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绿我一直觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同为一年级就应该不分组别  变得更要好才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Monaka也是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车即将到站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就从明天开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时间的话一起去吃甜食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从计划表上看实在是没那时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  别说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上6点就开始练习了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为丽奈不会喜欢和大家一起回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你之前说过类似的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是讨厌强迫自己和不喜欢的人交好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我并不讨厌川岛同学和加藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候我感觉到丽奈有一点变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过选拔得知了香织学姐和优子学姐的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即便如此仍想要变得与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着什么  丽奈也许也有她自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然冬装很热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去全国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你竞赛会获得金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉爸爸以后他也很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐虽然手机没打通  但她一定也会替你开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  那孩子以前也是演奏乐器的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概已经没兴趣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请欣赏  清良女子高中吹奏部的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这所高中很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  全国金奖的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和这样的学校比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是等我们能去全国之后的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡乱的头发没梳好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样练习没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多也要清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教员室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有音乐室的钥匙是开不了门的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天黄前同学也在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  音乐室的钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的话铠冢学姐已经先拿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门应该已经开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠冢同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担当双簧管的铠冢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她总是比我来得早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道早来是为了和泷老师说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈这种地方真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晨练也是我早来的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音很好听  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有些冷漠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 今天是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…铠冢学姐总是来得这么早吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真喜欢练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双簧管的声音被形容为优美的女声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅调音困难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最细的地方内径只有4毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气息的调整需要相当的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是它被成为最难的木管乐器的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到她会是这么冷谈的学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  我倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有些地方有点像丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  没什么大的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  今天黄前也一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事  坐着继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来铠冢学姐好像和优子学姐关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  两个人经常在一起说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实丽奈说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙你暑假作业做完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一半左右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  我一点都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  盂兰盆节有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起做不？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎么  总让人很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  你是低音组的一年级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  希美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么自作主当
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了在七班等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄出奇怪的举动把事情闹大了麻烦的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用道谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  刚看到的能对明日香学姐保密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此  但这却让我非常在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得是来看府大赛人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找明日香学姐有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问了也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐也不可能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出声来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么马上开始合奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前今天有个人想介绍给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是未婚妻？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是这所学校的OB  是打击乐器的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假期间他会来指导你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专家？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫桥本真博  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外号是小桥本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样和泷在大学可是同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于泷有什么想知道的就尽管问我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？ 反应好冷谈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多余的事情就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷肯定很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么没女生为他着迷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  吹奏部以外的女生确实会着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受吹奏部女生欢迎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉  泷以前嘴上就不留情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你多说多余的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对新任教练没兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人伤心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  打击乐组
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上开始严格训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要集中才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里几乎没有换气的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心就加快了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(834,990)}cunning breath
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮流换气怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后藤  你是在哪里换气的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个休止符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨子也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那后藤就在两小节之后换气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个乐句梨子不用勉强吹完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低音大提琴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(742,990)}Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿辉·川岛是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么注意刚才的地方再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子·黄前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天注意力都不集中  发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉姐姐吧  我不会使坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会使坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了快说！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子遇上什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想和学姐谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么  恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:22:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于恋爱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能先听我说完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我问你  这是找我私人谈的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是找副部长谈的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者都是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.04,0:24:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最讨厌竞赛会了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.74,0:24:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.70,0:25:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了高中我们一定要拿金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.28,0:25:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.30,0:25:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧  这才只是府大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.44,0:25:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南中是银奖
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.74,0:25:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.40,0:25:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得他们去年去了关西大赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.00,0:25:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.38,0:25:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:25:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说的是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:25:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.66,0:26:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了高中要拿金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.02,0:26:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一起拿金奖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.32,0:26:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.48,0:26:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让希美回吹奏部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.70,0:26:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  这跟我说也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.76,0:26:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是副部长  一个微不足道的中间管理职
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.26,0:26:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.58,0:26:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要明日香学姐的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.60,0:26:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.90,0:26:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.34,0:26:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没有明日香学姐的许可就不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.26,0:26:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样和我说  只会让我困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.00,0:26:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.16,0:26:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.30,0:26:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.94,0:26:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是练习时间
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.44,0:27:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能请你回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.67,0:27:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望一年级生能先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.07,0:27:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有话要谈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就只有一年级被排除在外
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.39,0:27:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.94,0:27:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事之前也发生过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.78,0:27:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.40,0:27:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和去年大批二年级退部的事情有关
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.21,0:27:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是吹奏部的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.28,0:27:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很想知道发生了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.42,0:27:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.34,0:27:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三天
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.55,0:27:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美学姐都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.40,0:27:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.28,0:27:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.66,0:27:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却每天都来这里等我们练习结束
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.51,0:27:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美学姐就那么想要回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.00,0:28:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  为什么不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.68,0:28:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此休庭
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.84,0:28:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要继续练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.80,0:28:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪和希美是朋友  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.50,0:28:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  希美并非是为了能参加竞赛会什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.04,0:28:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我只是想帮大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.80,0:28:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了  我没有决定权的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.62,0:28:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我也想得到学姐的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.40,0:28:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我个人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.94,0:28:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.20,0:28:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.24,0:28:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不赞成你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.26,0:28:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对这个部没有益处
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.90,0:28:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望你不要再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.92,0:28:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.50,0:28:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.56,0:29:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.74,0:29:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是希美又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.56,0:29:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.56,0:29:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香有告诉过我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.20,0:29:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.61,0:29:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…一言难尽…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.44,0:29:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  你们一年级不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.16,0:29:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专心练习就好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.64,0:29:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样说我们反而更在意没法好好练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.16,0:29:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.68,0:29:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你们再怎么期待  我也不会说什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.80,0:29:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你们应该知道去年有很多部员退部了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.84,0:29:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.96,0:29:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中大半是南中毕业的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.24,0:29:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.44,0:29:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.84,0:29:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美和夏纪都是南中的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.02,0:29:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以事情才会那么复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.98,0:29:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南中吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.14,0:29:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得他们今年也获得了初中部门的金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.70,0:29:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是废金
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.52,0:30:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们初二的时候他们是拿的银奖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.26,0:30:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时很多人很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.10,0:30:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说南中竟然只拿了银奖
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.77,0:30:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过夏纪学姐那时候不是吹奏部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.36,0:30:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.82,0:30:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我看着觉得她们两个关系不错
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.65,0:30:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说优子学姐和铠冢学姐也是南中毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.40,0:30:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.08,0:30:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  所以才会关系不错
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.49,0:30:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看着后藤学长和梨子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.50,0:30:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然对前辈们来说  去年的事情影响很大
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.90,0:30:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年级的人尤其不愿意提起这事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.14,0:30:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一提到这事就很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.76,0:30:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是  毕竟同年级的人一下子退出了近一半
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.94,0:30:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然很受打击了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.86,0:30:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那样退出的人现在突然说要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.54,0:30:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然大家都会很反感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.56,0:30:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.96,0:31:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是明日香学姐是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.64,0:31:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不光是因为这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.26,0:31:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3秒规则
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.54,0:31:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还是别吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.86,0:31:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来明天是烟花大会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.30,0:31:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.20,0:31:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家就能看得到  虽然有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.06,0:31:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.48,0:31:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该会和家人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.48,0:31:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绿说她也是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.00,0:31:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.28,0:31:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.76,0:31:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.91,0:31:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.62,0:31:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.70,0:31:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.77,0:31:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.78,0:31:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.78,0:31:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是觉得去不去无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.75,0:31:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要和我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.38,0:32:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道丽奈你在害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.70,0:32:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不太习惯邀请别人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.39,0:32:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是邀请了我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.20,0:32:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别笑嘻嘻的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.88,0:32:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦  没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.22,0:32:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比啰嗦  就说去不去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.45,0:32:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.20,0:32:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣放哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.84,0:32:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你要穿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.26,0:32:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.22,0:32:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.22,0:32:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这什么反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.96,0:32:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.16,0:32:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来至少给我敲个门
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.36,0:32:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.34,0:32:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.66,0:32:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你要去关西大赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.90,0:32:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.36,0:32:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.82,0:32:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.74,0:32:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.41,0:33:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是早起就睡不醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.26,0:33:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没习惯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.24,0:33:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要点时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.84,0:33:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.58,0:33:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是明静工科吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.58,0:33:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.83,0:33:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师完全没注意到我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.23,0:33:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他是在仔细考虑我们的不足之处
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.00,0:33:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们的演奏必须要胜过明静工科才行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.91,0:33:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明静吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.74,0:33:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们今年也是种子校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.82,0:33:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  毕竟这些年他们都进入了全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.62,0:33:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.28,0:33:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.88,0:33:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.16,0:33:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.28,0:33:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.34,0:34:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.60,0:34:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.36,0:34:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.36,0:34:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.20,0:34:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和她们两个关系不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.12,0:34:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.30,0:34:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗  学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.82,0:34:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…谁知道呢  学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.06,0:34:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…也说不清是好还是不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.12,0:34:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.10,0:34:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  一般
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.31,0:34:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一般学姐和学妹的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.48,0:34:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.47,0:34:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去外面练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.96,0:34:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.80,0:34:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明发生了那么多事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.64,0:35:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是对部内的人际关系不关心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.34,0:35:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.36,0:35:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这也是你的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.26,0:35:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.06,0:35:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于希美的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.84,0:35:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.26,0:35:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.04,0:35:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美她  好像有来说想回到部里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.91,0:35:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.78,0:35:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.56,0:35:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始小号的进入方式有些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.26,0:35:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是pa那样拖沓的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.00,0:35:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是从一开始很有气势地pang一下进入
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.04,0:35:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.30,0:35:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  极强音的声音有些浑浊不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.10,0:36:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保证音色响亮  优美
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.68,0:36:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.04,0:36:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上铠冢学姐那害怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.84,0:36:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我脑海中一直挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.66,0:36:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然有一部分原因是她一直以来都面无表情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.86,0:36:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  名来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.66,0:36:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打击乐开始的鼓滚奏准确了不少  感觉到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.52,0:36:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的时候乍一听还行
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.10,0:36:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有些粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.88,0:36:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.08,0:36:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然之前泷老师也指出过好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.88,0:36:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在总算抓到感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.70,0:36:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.44,0:36:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以再多佩服我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.90,0:36:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他还有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.34,0:36:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.05,0:36:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整体的演奏有些过于矜持  温和了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.96,0:36:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉大家平时的那种客套影响了整个演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.74,0:36:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要互相更厚脸皮一些才好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.18,0:36:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么意见  不要顾虑互相交流
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.26,0:36:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.36,0:36:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.53,0:37:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么刚才的地方再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.85,0:37:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为他只是个比较有趣的老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.56,0:37:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥本老师不愧是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.18,0:37:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让各组有什么意见互相交流  我觉得这主意好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.28,0:37:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.56,0:37:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我们以前几乎没做过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.02,0:37:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.72,0:37:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有去年的事  大家这方面都很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.29,0:37:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.72,0:37:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也不能永远顾忌那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.34,0:37:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们改头换面重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.06,0:37:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘拿水瓶了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.34,0:37:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘在音乐室了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.96,0:37:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能在走廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.58,0:37:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.74,0:37:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠冢学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.82,0:37:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.56,0:37:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.30,0:37:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.96,0:38:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去医务室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.90,0:38:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是不知道门还开不开着
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.16,0:38:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.06,0:38:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你脸色很差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.94,0:38:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.47,0:38:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.26,0:38:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是南中长笛的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.76,0:38:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.50,0:38:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是别勉强自己比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.67,0:38:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听见这个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.18,0:38:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你是吹悠风的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.02,0:38:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.90,0:38:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心  这是我自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.60,0:38:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想吹一下  就带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.00,0:38:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  你们今天结束得好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.18,0:38:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有烟花大会  所以已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.44,0:39:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明日香学姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.82,0:39:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  应该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.54,0:39:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.56,0:39:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长笛吹得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.06,0:39:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.30,0:39:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在南中要是没有自己的乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.74,0:39:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能吹长笛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.08,0:39:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以让父母给我买了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.44,0:39:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很喜欢长笛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.90,0:39:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.92,0:39:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢  很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.72,0:39:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.38,0:39:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样比较漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.02,0:39:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么紧我怎么大吃特吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.38,0:39:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是又胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.89,0:39:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.90,0:39:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.76,0:39:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.36,0:39:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐回那边了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.78,0:39:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.18,0:39:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉她也总是来去无踪的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.14,0:40:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.74,0:40:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿浴衣也没说的那么凉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.66,0:40:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.60,0:40:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.58,0:40:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.08,0:40:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.30,0:40:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.32,0:40:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不太敢和你走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.20,0:40:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.86,0:40:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.90,0:40:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.18,0:40:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.12,0:40:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色夏威夷味的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.14,0:40:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.20,0:40:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羊角包鲷鱼烧和印度三角炸饺
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.70,0:40:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  有那种东西卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.60,0:40:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去买刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.98,0:40:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去买鲷鱼烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.16,0:40:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要草莓味的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.64,0:40:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.06,0:41:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  这附近有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.46,0:41:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  原来你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.61,0:41:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.46,0:41:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃炒面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.96,0:41:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  炒面很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.16,0:41:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,县祭…一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.21,0:41:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟着来的话  让你跟着也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.02,0:41:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂你也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.78,0:41:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.70,0:41:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  又没和你们一起的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.36,0:41:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.17,0:41:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.30,0:41:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得没骨气的男人不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.21,0:41:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应那么平淡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.86,0:41:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}宇治川烟花大会即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.28,0:41:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  草莓味的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.00,0:41:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速射3号烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.49,0:41:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连发开始
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.16,0:41:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源氏物语  跨越千年的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.90,0:41:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在将复苏于此
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.62,0:42:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.80,0:42:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没这么认真看过烟花了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.16,0:42:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟去年要升学考
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.30,0:42:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你那么大一口的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3秒规则
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.70,0:42:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不吃  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.68,0:42:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来小时候和姐姐像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.94,0:42:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈你  对小号还真是情有独钟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.68,0:42:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.98,0:42:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为喜欢小号？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.66,0:42:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.52,0:42:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.24,0:42:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天看到希美学姐在吹
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.08,0:42:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习结束后吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.44,0:42:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.44,0:42:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她聊了会  她说自己非常喜欢长笛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.50,0:42:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么明日香学姐不同意她回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.36,0:43:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想要那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.52,0:43:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在让她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.06,0:43:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扰乱了部里的安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.72,0:43:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会对关西大赛造成影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.58,0:43:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得明日香学姐的判断是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.80,0:43:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那么喜欢  却无法和大家一起演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.90,0:43:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很让人难受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.43,0:43:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怪就怪她自己退部
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.22,0:43:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为退部会怎么样她自己应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.00,0:43:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.88,0:43:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得退部就是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.35,0:43:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不清楚是因为有讨厌的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.22,0:43:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是因为有讨厌的同级生  亦或是处于自己的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.20,0:43:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之她选择了逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.81,0:43:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话绝对不会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.44,0:43:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的话就用实力让他们臣服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.06,0:43:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她做不到这点而退部  就是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.83,0:43:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有丽奈的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.80,0:43:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  一般不应该都这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.96,0:43:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们会进入全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.90,0:44:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有一颗想要变得与众不同的心
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.59,0:44:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进了全国大赛就能变得与众不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.48,0:44:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.66,0:44:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这都没法做到无法变得与众不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.62,0:44:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.82,0:44:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能一起来真好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.14,0:44:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.40,0:44:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.96,0:44:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.46,0:44:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.84,0:44:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.84,0:44:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.16,0:44:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要到压台大戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.90,0:44:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请欣赏王朝绘卷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.57,0:44:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速射5号烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.28,0:44:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连发开始
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.10,0:44:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源氏浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.14,0:44:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光源氏永存
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.35,0:45:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时光并非永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.97,0:45:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会和最珍视的朋友分开
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.06,0:45:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.02,0:45:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都会转瞬即逝成为过去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.06,0:45:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能把现在这个瞬间放进容器冷藏起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.16,0:45:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来  就无需害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.18,0:45:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.62,0:46:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
